text: I'm on the wrong road aren't I?
Don't want to go to Ringwood or Woodchester do we?
Can't get there, this road has taken us out of our way hasn't it?
We'll have to do a little  --
--pas de deux here and turn the car around.
--The number of times I come off this roundabout onto the wrong road, it's
It's alwa- it's always the same isn't it?
It's just one of my habits I think.
